Author: MissouriMiner
Title: [Bounty] FAIR.GAME bounty is coming!!!!(Ended)
Body: FAIR.GAME- the very first decentralized fair game platform in the world! Campaign has ended , we are planning new campaign , please keep an eye on . Fair.Game Bounty Program  Based on Ethereum, Fair.game uses decentralized technology and smart contract to ensure the fairness of games. Fair.Game will be launched globally in different languages and multi-terminal versions such as WEB, Mobile APP (IOS, Android, PC). Fair.Game combines the “open, fair and just” features of blockchain and online games in an innovative way. It eliminates various problems in traditional games such as blackbox operation, non-transparent numerical algorithm and inequality among players. The platform will significantly increase the trust of the players and the fees that paying players are willing to spend on the game.  Please join Telegram chat group https://t.me/fairgameonline  Bounty program is open.  The total bounty pool available is 1,200,000 Fair Tokens, equivalent to 0.1% of the overall Fair token supply.  After the end of the bounty campaign, the tokens will be distributed to all participants according to their respective stakes.  Total Bounty Pool will be divided As Follows: (made some changes , added in a 3.33% airdrop and reduced the signature campaign share)    Twitter 20%, Facebook 20%, Telegram referral 10%, publications 20%, signature 11.666%, translation and community moderation 15%, airdrop 3.33%)  FOR AIRDROP, REFER TO THIS LINK:    TWITTER CAMPAIGN  Earn Tokens as a Reward for Tweeting about Fair.Game and for Retweeting @FairGameOnline announcements. LIMIT TO FIRST 1000 SIGNUPS.  Payment:  20% of Total Bounty will be allocated to Twitter  Tier 1: Having 250+ followers : 1 stake/week Tier 2: Having 500+ followers : 2 stakes/week Tier 3: Having 5,000+ followers: 10 stakes/week Tier 4: Having 25,000+ followers: 20 stakes/week  How to do it: 1.   Follow us here:  Twitter 2.   Make at least 5 retweets/tweets a week, essentially all the important announcements, with hashtag #fairgameonline. 3.   Register with the form: here 4.   In the end of every week fill in the form to provide us with the links to your retweets. week 1, week 2 5.   The tweets must not be removed from your personal Twitter until the end of the Bounty campaign. The posts must be public. 6.   Twitter accounts must be original. Fake, dead, inactive and bot accounts will not be accepted. 7.   Joining with multiple accounts is not allowed. Users found to be using multi accounts, will be blacklisted. 8.   The number of your stakes is displayed in this spreadsheet, this will be updated every week on Sunday. 9.   We DO NOT update the number of your followers. It is fixed after your registration.  Rules:  1. Twitter audit must be equal to or better than 85% (will use twitteraudit.com to check) 3. Don't post everything in 1 day, you are supposed to make the tweets constructive and not simply spam. 4. There will be no changing of payment addresses, so be sure it is correct  FACEBOOK CAMPAIGN Earn Tokens as a Reward for liking Fair.Game Facebook Page and sharing Fair.Game Official Announcements. LIMIT TO FIRST 1000 SIGNUPS.  Payment:  20% of Total Bounty will be allocated to Facebook  Tier 1: Having 400+ friends: 2 stakes Tier 2: Having 2000+ friends: 10 stakes Tier 3: Having 5000+ friends: 20 stakes  How to do it： 1.   Like and follow our Facebook Page here: Facebook 2.   Make a post about the Fair Token Sale and include our website link 3.   Fill this Form: Register here 4.   Share posts from Fair.game facebook page at least 3 times a week. 5.   In the end of every week fill in the form to provide us with the links to your reposts. Week 1, week 2 6.   Account must be open as a Public Profile and all Posts shared need to be public as well. 7.   Facebook accounts must be original. Fake, dead, inactive and bot accounts will not be accepted. 8.   Joining with multiple accounts is not allowed. Users found to be using multi accounts, will be blacklisted. 9.   The number of your stakes is displayed in this spreadsheet, this will be updated every week on Sunday. 10.   We DO NOT update the number of your followers. It is fixed after your registration.  Telegram referral Earn Tokens as a reward for inviting friends into the Telegram channel. Payment: 10% of total Bounty Pool will be allocated to Telegram referral; One stake per invite and one person can invite up to 10 other friends. How to do it： 1.   Join Telegram: here 2.   And invite your friends and fill in the form here. Just fill in the form once with all your invited friends’ user name. Duplicate entries will be disqualified. 3.   One person cannot be invited by two people 4.   One person can invite up to 10 other people. 5.   The number of your stakes is displayed in this spreadsheet, this will be updated every week on Sunday.  Publications Campaign Earn Tokens as a Reward for creating quality Reviews, Articles or Videos about Fair.Game actual gaming experience on Fair.Game platform. LIMIT TO FIRST 100 SIGNUPS. Payment: 30% of Total Bounty Pool will be allocated for Publications Campaign. High Quality: 25 stakes Good Quality: 10 stakes Normal Quality: 5 stakes Low Quality: 0 Stakes The numbers of Views will be taken into account in defining the Quality. How to do it： 1.   To send us a link to the publication or video, fill this form. 2.   All content must be original. Copying and translating other’s articles, as well as using other’s staff like videos, images, etc., is prohibited and will lead to disqualification. 3.   You can use our official images, logo, graphics and other published on our website and in the ANN thread. 4.   Articles must be longer than 500 characters. 5.   Videos must be at least 1 minute long. 6.   The article or description of the video must contain at least 1 link to our website or 1 link to the Whitepaper. The article or description must also contain a link to your BTT profile in order to prove your authorship. 7.   Blogging platforms like Medium, Steemit, Newbium, etc. are allowed. You can post on other platforms but we must be able to track the number of viewers. 8.   The number of your stakes is displayed in this spreadsheet. 9.   Manager and the Owners will have the rights to change any rules, or make any changes if necessary.  Signature Campaign Join our Signature Campaign to help spread the word about Fair.Game on Bitcointalk. In return for your contribution you will be rewarded Tokens. Only members ranked Jr. Member and above are accepted. LIMIT TO FIRST 500 SIGNUPS. Payment: 11.66% of Total Bounty Pool Will be Paid for Signature Campaign Participants Payment will be based on weekly stakes: Jr Member: 1 stakes / Week Member: 2 stakes / Week Full Member and above: 3 stakes / Week How to do it： 1.   To take part in the Signature bounty campaign, apply in this form. 2.   The signature codes and the avatar can be found here. 3.   The Signature must be held until the end of the campaign. In case that you remove the signature in the middle of the campaign, you are disqualified. 4.   Your need to make at least 8 constructive posts each week. 5.   Eligible are posts over 100 characters. Posts shorter than 100 characters are not counted. 6.   Posts must be constructive and On-topic. Spamming, low quality posts, copy paste and off topic posts will not be counted. 7.   Spammers and multi-accounts will be banned and disqualified. 8.   Receiving negative trust or ban during your participation in our campaign will result in you being disqualified from our campaign receiving nothing. 9.   The number of your stakes is displayed in this spreadsheet. 10.   Accounts with negative trust are not accepted.  Translation and community moderation Campaign Join our Translation Campaign to help spread the word about Fair.Game on Bitcointalk. In return for your contribution you will be rewarded Tokens. Only one translation per language is accepted, our admin will contact you from telegram @mike_player once your participation is selected. Payment: 15% of Total Bounty Pool Will be Paid for translation and community moderation Campaign Translator: 10 stakes per language. Languages needed: Japanese, Korean, Polish, Spanish, and Russian, German, French, Italian, Hindi, Indonesian, etc. We are also recruiting 10 community moderators (already recruited, so telegram moderators are not open for application any more) How to do it： 1.   To take part in the Translation bounty campaign, apply in this form. 2.   The translation must finish in five days. 3.   The number of your stakes is displayed in this spreadsheet.
